twitch_info.title: I Wanna Kill The Kamilia 3 - Stage 3 Speedrun in 1:47:31
twitch_info.description:
Pretty good run, some really good sections and some really bad sections. First 2 bosses were good but the chokes on The Guy were real. Might try to speedrun up to Boss Rush in the future.
